  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Transfusion of RBC is associated with post operative infections. Our hypothesis is that
      stored blood could be related with increased post operative infection risk. Surgical patients
      transfused during the operation or immediately after will be included in our study. Patients
      will receive fresh or old blood during the whole recovery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
